The paper deals with finding relevant patterns in a knowledge base for user-given keyword queries, which involves techniques from database systems (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of knowledge graphs and graph-based algorithms also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions text labeling and processing, which are common in natural language processing (cs.CL) and deep learning (cs.DL).
